=== 饮食 ===
{{main|阿根廷飲食}}
除了欧洲常见的-{zh-hans:意; zh-hk:意; zh-tw:義;}-大利麵、香肠和甜点，阿根廷人也享有各色本土菜式与[[克里奥尔人|克里奥尔]]菜式。包括[[南美烤饺子|南美烤饺子]]和阿根廷的国菜－[[阿薩多|阿薩多]]与{{tsl|en|locro|洛克罗}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.viaresto.clarin.com/Notas/El-asado-660.aspx|title=El asado|work=Via Restó|date=2010-04-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203103920/http://viaresto.com/Notas/El-asado-660.aspx|archivedate=2013-12-03|deadurl=yes|accessdate=2014-06-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.argentina.ar/_es/turismo/C791-gastronomia.php|title=Argentina–Gastronomia|publisher=Argentina – Portal oficial de promoción de la República Argentina|date=2008-06-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080727003909/http://www.argentina.ar/_es/turismo/C791-gastronomia.php|archivedate=2008-07-27|deadurl=yes|accessdate=2014-06-25}}</ref>。洛克罗是玉米、大豆、肉类、洋葱和葫芦的杂烩。而乌米塔以玉米碎、辣椒、洋葱、番茄等材料制成，类似于粽子。这个国家有着世界最高的[[紅肉|紅肉]]消费量<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.choicesmagazine.org/2006-2/tilling/2006-2-12.htm|title=Modern Beef Production in Brazil and Argentina|last=Steiger|first=Carlos|publisher=Choices Magazine|year=2006|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202235801/http://www.choicesmagazine.org/2006-2/tilling/2006-2-12.htm|archivedate=2013-12-02|deadurl=yes|accessdate=2014-06-25}}</ref>，传统的阿根廷[[烤肉|烤肉]]使用各种肉类，特别是[[牛肉|牛肉]]、[[羊肉|羊肉]]、[[乔利佐|乔利佐]]、[[牛犊胸腺|牛犊胸腺]]、[[粉腸|粉腸]]和[[血腸|血腸]]。{{sfn|McCloskey|Burford|2006|p=79}}维也纳式的酥皮点心和用来填充[[蛋糕|蛋糕]]和[[薄烤饼|薄烤饼]]的[[焦糖牛奶醬|焦糖牛奶醬]]是常见的甜点。加入巧克力、牛奶焦糖或水果泥的{{tsl|en | alfajores |西班牙夹心饼}}也很受欢迎。{{sfnm|1a1=Aeberhard|1a2=Benson|1a3=Phillips|1y=2000|1p=31|2a1=McCloskey|2a2=Burford|2a3=2006|2pp=80, 143}}[[阿根廷葡萄酒|阿根廷葡萄酒]]世界一流<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wine-pages.com/resources/argenexp.htm|title=About Argentine wine|publisher=Wine Pages|first=Tom|last=Cannavan|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121211132347/http://www.wine-pages.com/resources/argenexp.htm|archivedate=2012-12-11|deadurl=yes|accessdate=2014-06-25}}</ref>，是当地菜谱上不可或缺的佐餐酒，也是阿根廷两种官方国饮之一<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.ncu.edu.tw/~ncu7195/exhibit/90/ex3/info/04.htm |title = Ley No. 26870 – Declárase al Vino Argentino como bebida nacional, 2 de agosto de 2013, B.O., (32693), 1 |accessdate = 2013-08-02 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20041216234233/http://www.ncu.edu.tw/~ncu7195/exhibit/90/ex3/info/04.htm |archivedate = 2004-12-16 }}</ref>。[[马尔贝克|马尔贝克]]、{{tsl|en|Torrontés|托龙特}}、[[赤霞珠|赤霞珠]]、[[西拉葡萄|西拉]]和[[莎当妮|莎当妮]]是最抢手的几个国际品种{{sfn|McCloskey|Burford|2006|pp=230, 252, 261–262, 265}}。[[马黛茶|马黛茶]]是阿根廷的另一种官方国饮，在阿根廷国内可普遍见于课堂、聚会、公车等各种场合<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.ncu.edu.tw/~ncu7195/exhibit/90/ex3/info/04.htm |title = Ley No. 26871 – Declárase al Mate como infusión nacional, 2 de agosto de 2013, B.O., (32693), 1 |accessdate = 2013-08-02 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20041216234233/http://www.ncu.edu.tw/~ncu7195/exhibit/90/ex3/info/04.htm |archivedate = 2004-12-16 }}</ref>。
